page.title: 11A Day in My Life June 28th
page.content: I got up at 8.00 I went down stairs I had some cereal.I got dressed and watched televison .I went to school in the car and took my bike as well so I could bike home after school.After the register we had a maths test,and when break time came I went outside and played a game called bulldog.The object of the game was to get from one side of the playground to the other without being tagged.After break I did english,spelling workshop and some more maths .At lunch time we all went into the hall and had lunch I had sandwiches .Straight after lunch we went outside for play time I practised running on the school track.
